title: Trump campaign rally in Melbourne, Fla., begins soon
text:
4 
Hard to know what to expect given Pr*sident Trump’s latest public encounters. Perhaps he will let us know who else is on his enemies list. 
You can watch here if you have the stomach for it and nothing better to do with your weekend, like scrubbing toilets. 
The Resist: Melbourne people are on line here . 
If you yourself are there and have Tweets or video of the doings, join us in the comments. Here’s the crowd awaiting the arrival of the Orange Menace in the AeroMod hangar.
